National Technology Plan 1995 (1991-1995) Science & Technology 2000 (1995-2000) Science & Technology 2005 (2001-2005) Science & Technology 2010 (2006-2010) Research, Innovation & Enterprise 2015 (2011-2015) Research, Innovation & Enterprise 2020 (2016-2020) Research, Innovation & Enterprise 2025 (2021-2025) A DIVERSIFIE­D PORTFOLIO The global pace of digitalisa­tion has accelerate­d, and greater value has been placed on resilience and sustainabi­lity. Science, technology and innovation will be critical to overcoming Covid-19, and in enabling us to emerge stronger. Talent developmen­t $2.2b (9%) Mission-oriented research
